videos.description: Auburn's Malik Dunbar goes up strong to bank in a contested layup for the and-1.
videos.headline: Dunbar takes on two defenders for tough and-1 finish

videos.description: Admiral Schofield takes the ball away from Chuma Okeke and goes up for the layup, adding a trip to the foul line.
videos.headline: Schofield turns steal into and-1 layup

videos.description: Auburn drains 3-pointers on three straight possessions to take a commanding lead over Tennessee.
videos.headline: Auburn gets hot from 3-point land

videos.description: Bryce Brown and Chume Okeke each drain five 3-pointers as Auburn cruises past Tennessee 84-64 to win its first SEC title since 1985.
